metadata.name: Give me color.
metadata.description:
This is a high resolution portrait of Pablo "Juju" Callard, taken in August of 2020 in Asbury Park, New Jersey.

Title: Give Me Color  
Artist: Nick Kiefer  
Edition: 30/30  
Size: 5395px x 8093px  
Location: Asbury Park, New Jersey
